---
syntax: bash
tags: [ "personal", "docker" ]
---
# Require Bash alias added to hogehoge_oci
  
  baseDIR=`${HOME}/git_projects/work`
  ```
  alias hogehoge_oci="container_select <directory>/<container_name>"
  ```

# create and start container
  ```
  hogehoge_oci start
  ```
# stop and remove container
  ```
  hogehoge_oci stop
  ```

# restart container
  ```
  hogehoge_oci restart
  ```

